it.polimi.se2019.commons.utility

Interface MVEventDispatcher

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventDispatcher
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    View, ViewCLI, ViewGUI, VirtualView

    public interface MVEventDispatcher
extends EventDispatcher
    This class dispatches the events arriving from the model and directed to the view to the correct methods that will handle them. See EventDispatcher.
